            Gal Barby
          
          
            
              I am a statistics-economics student at the University
              of Haifa. Interested in data and teaching. I am an
              assistant lecturer in Econometrics and Microeconomics
              courses.
              my hobbies are sports, chess and playing guitar. I compete
              in powerlifting and prepare athletes for powerlifting
              competitions.
